<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>The British Embassy in Brussels has been holding meetings across Belgium to update UK nationals working and living in the country and answering their questions regarding the UK’s departure from the European Union. In our team’s continuous effort to reach as many UK nationals in Belgium as possible, we will be announcing further outreach meetings below.</p>

<h2 id="upcoming-uk-citizens-outreach-meetings-across-belgium">Upcoming UK citizens’ outreach meetings across Belgium</h2>

<div class="call-to-action">
<p>The event in Mons on Thursday 26 March has been cancelled in the light of of the ongoing and evolving situation regarding COVID-19. We hope to reschedule later in the year. In the meantime we are looking to organise Facebook Q&A’s in the coming weeks, where you will be able to submit your questions to us online.</p>
</div>

