<div class="call-to-action">
<p>Visit our <a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/living-in-belgium" class="govuk-link">Living in Belgium guide</a> for practical information, such as applying for residency. You can receive email alerts whenever the guide is updated by <a href="https://www.gov.uk/email-signup/?topic=/world/living-in-belgium" class="govuk-link">signing up here</a>.</p>
</div>

<p>To receive updates on what our team is up to, follow us on <a rel="external" href="https://www.facebook.com/ukinbelgium" class="govuk-link">Facebook</a> and <a rel="external" href="https://twitter.com/UKinBelgium" class="govuk-link">Twitter</a>.</p>
